701161f.title: Bronx: Grand Concourse - McClellan Street
701161f.text:
1155 to 1173 Grand Concourse, west side, north from but not
including McLellan Street, to but not including Tudor Place. W.P.A.
men are shown doing sidewalk repair work. The negative is reversed.
March 31, 1936.
Works Progress Administration.
Federal Art Project photo.
CREDIT LINE IMPERATIVE ON ALL REPRODUCTIONS.
